{"tid":812939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府大型工程屢爆貪污 愉翠苑短樁案最轟動","createTime":"2018-09-10T04:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T08:23:31.000Z","uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"82afbc015c25427cb86dbdc07fed023b97cc872d","tid":812939,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/6996647/realtime/article/20170520/56717119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F6996647%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170520%2F56717119&d=FzJLSKu%2FbYC3KX6Cw1qdVKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=75ca62fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F6996647%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170520%2F56717119&h=b9f9d3d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/6996647/realtime/article/20170520/56717119</a><br />\n<br />\n政府工務工程涉及龐大費用，往往成為貪污溫床。本港過往曾出現多次涉及政府大型工程的貪污案件，最轟動的要數1999至2000年間接連爆出公營房屋短樁醜聞。1999年，<span style=\"color: red;\">房屋署發現居屋天頌苑兩幢樓宇樁柱長度不合標準，<span style=\"color: red;\">須進行鞏固工程，樓宇延遲入伙十年</span></span>。廉署先後控告7人串謀訛騙等罪行，兩名工程師及助理工程監督被判監7年。<br />\n2000年，<span style=\"color: red;\">房屋署全面勘察轄下建築地盤後發現，沙田愉翠苑兩座<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嚴重沉降</span></span>，證實該兩幢樓宇嚴重短樁。其後廉署拘捕8名涉案人士，<span style=\"color: red;\">兩幢樓宇須拆卸重建</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。涉案承建商兩名董事被裁定串謀詐騙房委會罪名成立，被判入獄12年，上訴後獲減刑至10年；另一名地盤代表以同樣罪名，被判監3年半。<br />\n工程貪污案往往涉及偷工減料及監管人員收受利益縱容承建商牟利。2001年，黃大仙及飛鵝山兩幅路旁斜坡鞏固工程爆出醜聞，路政署人員在例行審核斜坡工程時，發現用作穩固斜坡的泥釘長度不符規定。廉署接手調查後發現承建商蓄意使用不合規格的物料，以降低成本及縮短施工時間，路政署監工亦有收受賄賂，包庇承建商，3名路政署監工及承建商等共10人被捕。<br />\n2009年，路政署被揭疑串同前署長級高官集體貪污，廉署代號「海龍捲」行動拘捕20人，包括一名已退休的土木工程拓展署署長及5名路政署官員，懷疑有私人建築商提供金錢和「必贏」賭波戶口，換取路政署官員監管過關，所涉多項道路維修合約逾億元。<br />\n<br />\n圓方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2b9b3ab822008ffd088d7793fceb62562d3006","tid":812939,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"97後明貪唔洗理icac 97前要貪都驚 要收收埋埋 依家真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140d41d8097a6fe961ce15119296d2b83677e2fb","tid":812939,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"中國特色管理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecb49c5b58d3b80c184080f402cad3157886c50","tid":812939,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d81efebb8755ace01e28800307e973e418ddc2","tid":812939,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"邊間建築先？"},{"pid":"bf13d79e07403081a02144624ccf02309d217460","tid":812939,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"當時個房署署長係苗學禮wo,  鬼佬黎架"},{"pid":"132cbfb0cf52a3fbe90b11d7c94842ac53aeada4","tid":812939,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed5574ca2e989ce74cb5c0dd18df91883b0fc48","tid":812939,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf13d79e07403081a02144624ccf02309d217460","tid":812939,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"當時個房署署長係苗學禮wo,  鬼佬黎架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"署長鬼識工程咩"}]}